# Cluster Map Status V4.4.12

## Release Title

Cluster Map Status V4.4.12

## Tag

v4.4.12

## Release Asset

Upload this ZIP to the release:

```text
Cluster_Map_Status_V4_4_12_EXE_Package.zip
```

## What Changed

- Restored Dashboard to the sidebar as the first tab.
- Dashboard is now the default first page.
- Dashboard has concept-style stat cards.
- Added compact dashboard preview area.
- Added action panel with Update Now, Test Webhook, and Check for Updates.
- Added countdown panel.

## Also Included

- About page with Updates, Progress Summary, and About tabs.
- Desktop shortcut repair support.
- GitHub update checker.
